      "block_type": "Equation",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Equation\"><math display=\"block\">R_i(t_1, t_2) = \\frac{P_i(t_2)}{P_i(t_1)} = 1 + r_i(t_1, t_2), i = 0, \\dots K</math>\n(2)</p>",
