    {
      "id": "/page/0/TextInlineMath/6",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\">Suppose an investor has <math display=\"inline\">w_t</math> units of capital at time <math display=\"inline\">t</math>, and that capital is fully invested in the assets, with the proportions invested in each asset given by <math display=\"inline\">x_i(t), i = 0, \\dots K</math>, where <math display=\"inline\">\\sum_{i=0}^{K} x_i(t) = 1</math>. Then an investment or trading strategy at time <math display=\"inline\">t</math> is the vector process</p>",
