      "id": "/page/0/Equation/9",
      "block_type": "Equation",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Equation\"><math display=\"block\">W(t_2) = w_{t_1} R'(t_1, t_2) X(t_1) = w_{t_1} \\sum_{i=0}^{K} R_i(t_1, t_2) x_i(t_1)</math>\n(4)</p>",
