      "id": "/page/1/Text/4",
      "block_type": "Text",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"Text\">The case usually discussed is the one in which the incremental returns are serially independent. So the maximization of <math display=\"inline\">E[G_n(X)]</math> is</p>",
