      "id": "/page/1/TextInlineMath/9",
      "block_type": "TextInlineMath",
      "html": "<p block-type=\"TextInlineMath\" class=\"has-continuation\">A variation on the Kelly strategy is the fractional Kelly strategy defined as <math display=\"inline\">\\tilde{X}_f = f\\tilde{X}^*, f \\ge 0</math>. The</p>",
